descriptionHtml:
[size=3]Hi everyone, here's my second Skyrim upload. It's another Breton/Elf looking character preset based on yet another character from Might and Magic Heroes VII. This time we have Yrbeth. (I forgot to take the circlet off while I was taking the screenshots :p )



Required:

Racemenu   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624[/url]﻿

SG eyebrows   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327[/url]﻿

KS Hairdos - HDT Physics   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363[/url]﻿

Eyes of beauty  [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722[/url]



Thank you to all of the fantastic modders for supplying the, you know.. mods, credit goes to:

Racemenu - expired6978
SG eyebrows - hellosanta
KS Hairdos - HDT Physics - Stealthic Khaos
Eyes of beauty - [/size][size=3]LogRaam



[/size][size=3]Here's a bit of information about Yrbeth's character from MMH7:[/size]

[i][size=3]Yrbeth was a child gifted with powers of focus and concentration beyond her years. Training in the eldritch arts like many of her kin, Yrbeth's ability to focus her powers permits her to accumulate more magical energies than is normally possible. The night before an important battle Yrbeth often goes sleepless, spending hours in meditation to prepare herself.[/size][/i]
author: ratman186
